===Etymology 5===
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=o|じょう}}
Alteration from ''sau'', itself an alternative reading of ''sa'' above, possibly influenced by an early variety of {{cog|cmn|-}} reading ''suǒ'' or {{cog|yue|-}} reading ''so²''.<ref name="KDJ"/> The shift from ''sau'' to ''jau'' (modern ''jō'') was probably the influence of the reading of synonymous character {{ja-l|錠}} (''jō'').

{{IPAchar|/sa/}} → {{IPAchar|/sau/}} → {{IPAchar|/d͡ʑau/}} → {{IPAchar|/d͡ʑoː/}}

